Fruit Snake for Chrome Extension is an exciting and fast-paced endless fruit-eating game that takes inspiration from the beloved classic snake video game. However, this colored version comes with a twist. In this game, players are challenged to navigate the snake quickly to collect various fruits. The objective is to gather as many fruits as possible to increase your remaining time. As the snake consumes fruits, it grows longer, allowing you to extend your gameplay. But be cautious! Running out of time will result in a game over. Additionally, you must avoid colliding with your own tail three times, as this will also end the game.

Experience the addictive gameplay of "Fruit Snake" for free by visiting the website https://googlesnake.org/. Challenge yourself to beat your high score and see how long you can keep the game going. Enjoy the thrilling adventure of guiding the snake to devour fruits and test your skills in this vibrant and engaging game.
